            "The reason behind the little bee in my logo: Melissa (Μελίσσα): In Greek, it means 'bee.' It comes from meli (μέλι), meaning 'honey'. The name Melissa was used in Greek mythology and ancient culture to refer to a nymph who discovered how to collect honey or a priestess of Demeter associated with bees.",
